{"tid":831963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「美魔女選美大賽」　47歲知性人妻奪冠","createTime":"2018-09-22T12:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:42:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0adc917fa42903b3ddae8c534a844aa9d8a79add","tid":831963,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"集結出35歲以上才色兼具的成熟女性，最終選出優勝者的「美魔女選美大賽」<br />\n9月19日在東京品川舉行終選拔，由47歲的梅本理慧奪下后冠。<br />\n <br />\n據《atpress》報導<br />\n美魔女選美大賽由光文社的女性月刊《美ST》舉辦<br />\n第一屆從2010年開始<br />\n主要為挑選「感受不到年齡的美貌以及知性美」的活動<br />\n今年為第九屆，進入最終決選的16人，在9月19日進行舞蹈、歌藝等特技表演<br />\n以及泳裝、洋裝等挑戰，並從「不受年齡影響的美貌」、「經驗累積淬鍊的內在美」<br />\n「一直追求美的好奇心跟向上心」、「無法自我滿足的社交能力」<br />\n這4點最為基準來審查。<br />\n <br />\n最終由16人裡面年紀最大，住在神奈川縣的47歲主婦梅本理慧奪冠<br />\n梅本理慧於京都出生，家裡除了丈夫外還有一個讀大二的小孩，身高167公分<br />\n奪冠後她說「我相當驚訝，因為我從沒想過可以拿到冠軍」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/200928_733e7edb28dd7ee35094b6b1ec54883c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F200928_733e7edb28dd7ee35094b6b1ec54883c.png&h=596d3e87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/201006_3682e25f4e7c3cb9700de5fc65c5e797.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F201006_3682e25f4e7c3cb9700de5fc65c5e797.png&h=00e97087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a21faad7d181afa8f40b908b61d628be81368f5","tid":831963,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"幾白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcae3970a85ce60ad4c8270abb0c7b5dd6751b3","tid":831963,"uid":67500,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"美熟女 &gt; 美少女"},{"pid":"a1eaa78eb9fa18364231b273c11e92b09bf69021",